Package: EpiReport
Type: Package
Title: ECDC Annual Epidemiological Report
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lore Merdrignac
Maintainer: Lore Merdrignac <l.merdrignac@epiconcept.fr>
Description: The EpiReport package allows the user to draft 
  the ECDC Annual Epidemiological Report for a given disease and in Microsoft Word format. 
  It is specifically designed to generate each disease-specific outputs 
  used in these reports, using ECDC Atlas export data.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
License: EUPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
